name: C4NC3R-22
description:
7H3 M0N7H 0F C4NC3R-22 is a special month. It is ruled by the moon. It is also the month of healing and overcoming limitations. You can connect to the energy of the month by meditating on the Aramaic letters embedded in this mixed media digital piece of art. I used a mix of personal video footage of myself and places in London and illustration. 

It is part of my Z0D14C-22 collection, 12 part collection. This is number 04. 

Throughout the year I will release one piece (3 eds / mp4) for each of the months. It is a mixed media project including sound and visuals created by me. 

For more updates on releases, please follow on Twitter or Instagram. 

Go to http://christianroman.studio for more info about my work. 

C4NC3R-22 by Christian Roman
